title: Enable Serial Communication Between KVM VMS in Nixos
tags: @zettel _method nixos kvm
roam-id: 1519d20d-ffcd-4b5e-a215-c470006546a6
type: text/markdown

- enable `"console=ttyS0"` kernel parameter

  ``` nix
  # /etc/nixos/configuration.nix
  boot = {
    kernelParams = [
      "console=ttyS0"
    ];
  };
  ```
